name: FramesPerspectiveOnCM
hasDescription: ["This should pick additional frames (wrt SubcaseOfFramesRelatedByCM) that are related to a source frame by an 'isAPerspectiveOn' relation."]
label: ['FramesPerspectiveOnCM']

name: SubcaseOfFramesRelatedByCM
hasDescription: ['The target and source frames are subcases of a CMs target and source frames', 'respectively.']
label: ['SubcaseOfFramesRelatedByCM']

name: TFrameIsRoleInSFrame
hasDescription: ["OR target frame us a subcase of a frame that's incorporated into source frame", 'Target frame is incorporated as a role in source frame', 'where the subcase relation may cascaded to an arbitrarily depth.']
label: ['TFrameIsRoleInSFrame']

name: FramesDirectlyRelatedByCM
hasDescription: ['The target and source frames are directly related by a CM.']
label: ['FramesDirectlyRelatedByCM']

name: TFrameUsesSFrame_1_2
hasDescription: ['Target frame is a subcase of or makes use of source frame', 'where those relations may occur once or twice in succession.']
label: ['TFrameUsesSFrame.1-2']

name: FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM_2
hasDescription: ['The target frame is a subcase descendent of a frame which is made use of by a frame which is a subcase descendant of the target frame of a CM.  The source frame is a subcase descendant of the source frame of a CM.']
label: ['FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM.2']

name: FramesMakeUseOfCM_2
hasDescription: ['The target and source frames are subcase descendants of frames that make use of the target and source frames of a CM.']
label: ['FramesMakeUseOfCM.2']

name: FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM_3
hasDescription: ['Target frame is a subcase descendant of a frame which is made use of by a frame which is a subcase descdendant of the target frame of a CM.  The source frame is a subcase descendant of the source frame of that CM OR it is the subcase of a frame which is made use of by a frame which is a subcase descendant of the source frame of the CM.']
label: ['FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM.3']

name: UsedByOtherFrame
hasDescription: ['There is a frame that makes use of both the target frame and source frame.']
label: ['UsedByOtherFrame']

name: TFrameUsesSFrame_3_4
hasDescription: ['with 3 or 4 such relations intervening between the frames.', 'Target frame is a subcase of or makes use of source frame']
label: ['TFrameUsesSFrame.3-4']

name: SubcaseOfSameFrame
hasDescription: ['with up to 2 subcase relations cascaded.', 'Target frame and source frame are subcases of the the same frame']
label: ['SubcaseOfSameFrame']

name: FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM
hasDescription: ['The target frame is made use of by a frame that is a subcase descendent of the target frame of a CM.  The source frame is a subcase descendent of the source frame of the CM.']
label: ['FramesRelatedAtHigherLevelByCM']

name: FramesMakeUseOfCM
hasDescription: ['Target and source frames make use of the target and source frames of a CM', 'respectively.']
label: ['FramesMakeUseOfCM']
